{"tid":1079631,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人愈大愈唔鐘意食放題？","createTime":"2019-03-27T05:31:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T12:47:35.000Z","uid":187852,"like":61,"dislike":188,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf5ae19eef43e13e56aa5ef00e9453e476296a2","tid":1079631,"uid":187852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:31:17.000Z","msg":"早幾日同女朋友去食放題韓燒<br />\n諗起細個會好鐘意，大時大節都想食放題<br />\n一食就3 round起、飲4-5罐野飲，重量不重質<br />\n而家調返轉，居然會怕果種飽到想嘔既感覺<br />\n就住就住黎食，叫到2nd round就開始頂唔順<br />\n寧願比多少少錢食逐樣叫又好食既<br />\n都唔食放題/任食<br />\n有冇巴絲都係咁？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> - 都係咁鐘意食放題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> - 放題/任食？不了"},{"pid":"02588d55219504538f68cbf03ebb93fc8883de10","tid":1079631,"uid":34777,"like":26,"dislike":3,"score":23,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:32:59.000Z","msg":"最主要覺得啲刺身唔太乾淨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寧願食啲貴啲但高質啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f62043ea11402dd8c5533f03731df5ed9cca9a7","tid":1079631,"uid":151245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:35:30.000Z","msg":"有無推介"},{"pid":"ca10e1f9d2d691ac83786dfb93b80aef0a2a2bf1","tid":1079631,"uid":16061,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:38:00.000Z","msg":"係因為大個仔搵到錢<br />\n細個無錢先任食"},{"pid":"2aede58ac8322376a151c7ae8136f0048850bb47","tid":1079631,"uid":60959,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:42:23.000Z","msg":"唔會，一樣係爆食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3df8d40131269a8b3464d994ae8d3250f86cacb8","tid":1079631,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:43:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd05c4fe22bd046e261b740fcdd359750647aed6","tid":1079631,"uid":38540,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"02588d55219504538f68cbf03ebb93fc8883de